scenes.description: Koseki Bijou, IRyS, and Ninomae Ina'nis performing an English cover of 'DIAMOND HEART' titled 'DIAMOND GIRLFRIEND' in a racing-themed stage.
The performance ends, and Biboo celebrates her victory in the race as the winner's coin appears.
A mysterious portal appears behind them, and they are sucked into it.
Biboo lands in a new area described as the 'Puzzle Stage' and prepares for the next challenge.
